1. Matrix Addition

Process of adding the corresponding elements of two or more matrices of the SAME order

\[A=\left[\begin{array}{cc}1&2\\ 3&4\end{array}\right]\quad B=\left[\begin{array}{cc}2&3\\ 4&5\end{array}\right]\]

\[A+B=\left[\begin{array}{cc}1+2&2+3\\ 3+4&4+5\end{array}\right]\]

\[=\left[\begin{array}{cc}3&5\\ 7&9\end{array}\right]\]

2. Matrix Subtraction

Process of subtracting the corresponding elements of two or more matrices of the SAME order

\[A=\left[\begin{array}{cc}2&4\\ 6&8\end{array}\right]\quad B=\left[\begin{array}{cc}2&3\\ 4&5\end{array}\right]\]

\[A-B=\left[\begin{array}{cc}2-2&4-3\\ 6-4&8-5\end{array}\right]\]

\[=\left[\begin{array}{cc}0&1\\ 2&3\end{array}\right]\]

